<h2 id="ministry-of-justice-press-office">Ministry of Justice press office</h2>

<p>Journalists with enquiries can call the news desk on 0203 334 3536.</p>

<p>The news desk is the point of contact for all breaking news and major developments, including interview requests, central co-ordination of departmental enquiries, facts, figures and statistics, statements and diary information.</p>

<p>The desk operates from 7am to 7pm, Monday to Friday. 
Emergency media calls (out-of-hours): 020 3334 3536 - you will be automatically diverted to the relevant duty officer.</p>

<p>If you are not a member of the media, please use the Ministry of Justice public enquiries line: 0203 334 3555.</p>

